<section class="bg-teal-900 py-20 text-white">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
		<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-amber-100">
			Loved by San Antonio Families
		</h2>
		
		<div class="bg-teal-800/50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-teal-700 relative">
			<div class="text-7xl text-teal-600/50 absolute top-4 left-6 font-serif leading-none">"</div>
			
			<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed italic text-gray-100 mb-8 relative z-10">
				Emote Academy was a Godsend to our family. Punnami and her staff take the time to figure out each child's needs and tailor their learning from there. The change I've seen in my son is astonishing. I would HIGHLY recommend Emote Academy!
			</p>
			
